{"tid":146373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲又現怪魚 似魚蝦混合體","createTime":"2017-03-07T04:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T14:09:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22cf10c270ee36ba5c148de48ab33e6efdac5f0c","tid":146373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">【神秘海洋】澳洲又現怪魚 似魚蝦混合體<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56394478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56394478&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6ef6292d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56394478&h=75c7ee98\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56394478</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488833585_fb8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488833585_fb8b.jpg&h=d2f376d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲漁民聲稱在北領地附近深海一處「秘密地點」，發現「魚蝦混合體」。<br />\n<br />\n漁民在達爾文對開澳洲和印尼海洋劃界附近的300米深海，發現那種外表像史前動物的怪魚。那種魚眼大大，表面黏糊糊，有小角凸出，而且有腳。漁民未見過，以為是海龍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488833586_6037.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488833586_6037.jpg&h=35f5f231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專家指這類魚屬魴鮄科，又稱角魚科，有幼腳方便在海床爬行，而在水中游動時，胸鰭一開一合就像鳥的翅膀在飛行一樣，故稱為「骨甲海中知更鳥」（armoured sea robin）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488833587_97c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488833587_97c8.jpg&h=323597d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"e88466253cf971b57a9b583e23f2ae148283e65f","tid":146373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4d81eefa3ab5f7c514eccddb82c15bc8a61e82","tid":146373,"uid":34260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"一家三口就咁比人類捉左上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df2b00bd46ac704b27e0d74a87e24fd0649fe94","tid":146373,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7882a770495e770a337a1f2d76093615a4594e1","tid":146373,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"似足新幹線列車車頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1937f14cfe42776f373cc9a02cbe45d5a0353e7a","tid":146373,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"瀬尿蝦 D朋友"},{"pid":"1b5edbe5304abe97be8d301089af773d837f0636","tid":146373,"uid":32149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"澳洲真係奇珍異獸集中地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58d7bf11d80a85bb8cd057df4c2454a0ad7081a","tid":146373,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"之後會見到有大陸post用返同一張圖話係日本輻射魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2756058b00838269950ffba9cd71b6294dfd62e7","tid":146373,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0ca75f87986c5674b55ab0e8f0941651733c4f3","tid":146373,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11: